        <sponsor name-id="S306">Mr. Menendez</sponsor> (for
			 himself, <cosponsor name-id="S282">Mr. Nelson</cosponsor>,
			 <cosponsor name-id="S253">Mr. Durbin</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="S259">Mr.
			 Reed</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S316">Mr. Whitehouse</cosponsor>)
